      %b estimated length of all occupants to aquarium size
    = link_to 'water changes', about_water_health_path(anchor: 'care_schedule')
    than recommended to try and keep you unhealthy elements at a safe level. It is also recommended that you
    \#{link_to "test your aquarium's water", about_water_health_path(anchor: 'water_test')}  more often.
